				<td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=4207&amp;sid=d1ee048d1884aa846d2667e515f8f9fe#4207"><img src="templates/EQ2Scouts/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Fri Sep 17, 2004 10:16 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: Who's got spirit? Not us.</span></td>
				<td valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=4207&amp;sid=d1ee048d1884aa846d2667e515f8f9fe"><img src="templates/EQ2Scouts/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>   </td>
